translation.en: We should've done this ourselves.
We know the king's palace better than your patsy does.
Teela hasn't failed us yet.
translation.es: Teela aún no nos ha fallado.

translation.en: She'll find what we seek.
With that sword, the Power of Grayskull
translation.es: Con esa espada, el poder de Grayskull pronto será nuestro.

translation.en: will soon be ours.
translation.es: el poder de Grayskull pronto será nuestro.

translation.en: How's the nation of Eternos this evening?
Quiet as a shadow, King Randor.
Never trust shadows, General.
You catch that game of modulok?
No, modulok's too complicated.
Running on your hands and passing with your feet?  No, thank you.
translation.es: ¿Correr con las manos y lanzar con los pies?

translation.en: I'll take it from here, Soldier.
Of course, General Dolos.
I'll take it from here, Soldier.
Evelyn better pay me this time.
Oh, come on!
'Word witch didn't say there'd be this many to choose from.
translation.es: La bruja no mencionó tantas opciones.

translation.en: - Okay. -
Which one of you is gonna give me that trademark Teela Grayskull tingle?
translation.es: ¿Cuál me dará el cosquilleo de Grayskull típico de Teela?

translation.en: I've been contracted to go through all this trouble to steal a--
translation.es: Todos estos problemas para robar una…

translation.en: Sword, Eternia, Grayskull, secrets, Eternia, Power,
Masters of the Universe, Masters of the Universe.
That was way more than a tingle.
Drop the sword!
I'll just put it right... here.
Did she just continue to steal?
Sorry.  I just needed my hands free to do... this.
translation.es: Necesitaba las manos libres para hacer esto.

translation.en: Oh, no!
How will we ever grab our swords with our other hands?
translation.es: ¿Cómo tomamos la espada con la otra mano?

translation.en: Oh, sorry. My thumb stuck.
Able to do... this!
Oh, yeah, much better.
Somebody stop her!
- You! Halt! - Get her now!
Go! Go! Get her!
Ah- ha- ha, one of my legs fell asleep, sorry.
Must you have brought your apprentice along?
You! Halt!
Duncan didn't bring the Royal Guard to the extraction point.
translation.es: Duncan no trajo a la Guardia al punto de extracción.

translation.en: Just sayin'.
Incoming!
What an unfortunate turn of events... for them.
No! They're just doing their jobs!
Give me the sword, Hand Witch.
That sword does not belong to her.
Start the engine, kid. This is a bust.
We're on our way to you.
The sword is right there.
Our key to universal unstoppable power is right there!
translation.es: ¡Nuestra llave al poder universal e imparable!

translation.en: We don't gotta find the sword again, just the girl.
translation.es: No necesitamos la espada, solo a la chica.

translation.en: Let's move.
Bring the sword to the champion.
What champion?
I have the Power!
The Power is ours It's in our so- o- o- o- o- o- o- o- o- oul
translation.es: Está en nuestra alma el poder.

translation.en: The Power is ours It's in our so- o- o- o- o- o- o- o- o- oul
translation.es: Está en nuestra alma el poder.

translation.en: The Power is ours
Hey, we'll find our purpose
translation.es: El poder es nuestro. Buscamos una misión.

translation.en: 'Cause we know we're worth it
And we'll be remembered
We are the defenders, defenders
- Oh - We fight for the win
We fight till the end
- We fight for the win - The Power is ours
translation.es: Luchamos hasta el final. - Para ganar. - Está en nuestra alma el poder.

translation.en: It's in our soul
translation.es: - Para ganar. - Está en nuestra alma el poder.

translation.en: Hang in there, Kitty. I've got you.
Just crawl onto my shoulders and we can both go home.
translation.es: Solo súbete y volveremos a casa.

translation.en: No.
What do you mean, no?
I don't want us to fall.
We won't fall.
We won't fall...
...if you get on my shoulders right now.
translation.es: si te subes a mis hombros.

translation.en: Did you, like, eat rocks today?
I thought they were potatoes.
Did they taste like potatoes?
I've never had a potato before.
- - How am I supposed to know?
You jump the rest of the way. What about you?
I'll be fine.
Dragonfly.
- No. - Dragonfly.
No, don't do it. Focus.
Dragonfly!
Adam, are you two done yet?
Or do you wanna hang out some more?
How long have you been there?
Long enough to work on that joke. Thought it might defuse the tension.
translation.es: Tuve tiempo de pensar esa broma pare relajarte.

translation.en: Way to take my mind off of imminent death, Krass. Thanks.
translation.es: Gracias por distraerme de una muerte inminente.

translation.en: What are best friends for?
You weren't on tracker duty today.
What are you doing out here? Cringer's missing,
and this part of the woods has the best snacks for grabbing,
so I figured why not start looking for him here?
Wait, did you just say Cringer was missing?
Kitty, did you come out here looking for your uncle?
translation.es: Gatito, ¿viniste a buscar a tu tío?

translation.en: Maybe.
He said he wanted to go hunting again.
translation.es: Dijo que quería ir a cazar.

translation.en: Puh! He can't hunt without claws.
Try telling him that.
Contain. Shut.
- - Push.
Release me, or incur the wrath of my tribe,
translation.es: Déjenme ir o enfrentarán la ira de mi tribu, Bestiópodos.

translation.en: you Beastopoid brutes.
translation.es: o enfrentarán la ira de mi tribu, Bestiópodos.

translation.en: Quarry talks like it is people.
Quarry talks like we are people.
Don't you poachers want more from life than caging and hurting animals?
Why not rise up against your keeper? Try living for yourselves.
translation.es: ¿Y si se rebelan? Tomen sus decisiones.

translation.en: Initiate capture.
An uprising would displease our keeper.
Query for quarry: what happened to you
translation.es: Recuerda. ¿Qué pasó la última vez que disgustaste al amo?

translation.en: when last you displeased our keeper?
translation.es: ¿Qué pasó la última vez que disgustaste al amo?

translation.en: Fair point, my subservient captors.
R'qazz will be most pleased to have you back in the fight pit.
translation.es: R'Qazz estará feliz de que vuelvas a su arena de combate.

translation.en: He may add your skull to his trophy belt after your loss.
translation.es: Puede usar tu cráneo como trofeo al derrotarte.

translation.en: Oh, what an honor.
Let me at those circuit brains. No time for the bots.
translation.es: - Les daré una paliza… - No hay tiempo.

translation.en: We gotta spring Cringer.
I knew you'd come for me.
We needed a faster ride home anyway. Stand back.
Hang on!
Initiate stowaway protocol.
Great plan! Now what?
You up for a game of ram- ball?
I'm wearing my helmet, ain't I?
Adam of the Tiger Tribe risks it all...
translation.es: Adam de la Tribu del Tigre arriesga todo

translation.en: ...to send Krass to the net.
Will she make the...
Have I mentioned how much I hate this game?
...goal?
Happy to see you too.
But hug me any tighter, and I'll let them keep you next time.
translation.es: pero si me abrazas así, no te vuelvo a rescatar.

translation.en: Wait. What happened to Krass?
Tiger Tribe for the win!
Cringer, next time you feel like
translation.es: ¡Cringer! La próxima vez que quieras pelear, avisa.

translation.en: taking on some Beastopoids, let us know, huh?
translation.es: La próxima vez que quieras pelear, avisa.

translation.en: Now, where would the fun in that be?
Tiger Tribe forever?
Tiger Tribe forever.
Why would you go hunting alone again?
Everyone in the tribe does their part.
translation.es: Aquí cada uno hace su parte.

translation.en: Even without my claws, I'd like to still do mine.
translation.es: Aún sin garras, me gustaría hacer mi parte.

translation.en: Spoken like a true Stripe.
I don't need a special tattoo to be a part of the tribe.
translation.es: No necesito un tatuaje para pertenecer.

translation.en: You keep saying that, but I never see you leave.
translation.es: Dices eso, pero nunca te vas.

translation.en: Now, now, Krass'tine.
Every lost soul the tribe adopts gets their stripes when they so choose.
translation.es: Cada miembro recibe sus rayas cuando lo elige.

translation.en: If Adam isn't ready to set aside his cuff and get his stripe,
translation.es: Si no está listo para dejar su brazalete,

translation.en: Adam isn't ready.
This is all I have from my life before.
translation.es: Es lo que me queda mi pasado.

translation.en: What if whoever lost me doesn't recognize me without this?
translation.es: ¿Y si ya no me reconocen sin esto?

translation.en: It's been ten years.
Ah, they probably stopped looking for you by now.
Whatever, helmet head.
Kitty, what you doing? There's a lady in the tree.
translation.es: - ¿Qué haces? - Hay una dama en el árbol.

translation.en: Um, can we help you, tree lady?
Uh, your village is full of cats.
translation.es: Tu aldea está llena de felinos.

translation.en: I'm apparently afraid of cats.
Then why did you come out here to where the Tiger Tribe lives?
translation.es: ¿Y por qué viniste al hogar de la Tribu del Tigre?

translation.en: A voice in my head told me to.
translation.es: ¿Me lo dijo una voz en mi cabeza?

translation.en: Ask it how much it knows about cats being able to climb trees.
Why?
I got her!
Adam. Teela.
Magic!
- What if she got caught? - We'd know.
I've been listening to the Royal security channels.
Right, because of all the crime we're doing.
translation.es: Claro. Por los delitos que cometemos.

translation.en: This is about revenge on the king,
We're not not doing crime, though.
translation.es: Pero no deja de ser un delito.

translation.en: You find her yet?
We're here. Descend.
Is that an actual poacher ship?
The sword doesn't want her found.
Think I can get these poacher bots up and running to hunt her scent.
translation.es: Haré que los bots cazadores la busquen.

translation.en: Do it. Find the traitorous whelp.
Apprentice, get to work.
Why aren't you afraid of magic like the rest of your people?
translation.es: ¿No le temes a la magia como los demás?

translation.en: To be clear, the cats don't like magic.
translation.es: A los felinos no les gusta.

translation.en: Why let yourself get captured?
You wouldn't understand.
Oh, because I'm from the jungle and you're from the city?
Believe me, you're from the city.
I am?
Yeah, your accent sounds like you were born into an upper family.
translation.es: Hablas como si vinieras de una familia superior.

translation.en: Just count your lucky stars you're out here and not back in the house that Randor built.
translation.es: Mejor estar aquí y no en la casa de Randor.

translation.en: You don't like the king?
No one likes the king, especially at street level...
translation.es: Nadie lo quiere, en especial en las calles,

translation.en: or below street level, which is where I usually am.
translation.es: o debajo de las calles, donde suelo estar.

translation.en: Randor won't do anything about all the poaching out here, so he's no friend of the tribe's either.
translation.es: Randor no controla la caza, así que las tribus no lo apoyan.

translation.en: And now that we're done bonding,
shouldn't you be getting back to doing whatever the voice in your head told you to?
translation.es: ¿no deberías hacer lo que te indica la voz en tu cabeza?

translation.en: Like I said... you wouldn't understand.
Try me.
That isn't jealousy I smell...  ...is it?
translation.es: Eso que huelo no son celos, ¿o sí?

translation.en: Oh, of course not.
Adam's like a brother to me. I'm just worried he's gonna leave.
translation.es: Adam es un hermano para mí. Me preocupa que se vaya.

translation.en: Some flashy magic wielder showing up isn't gonna help anything.
translation.es: La llegada de una maga presumida no ayuda en nada.

translation.en: And it's a problem we can't solve by ramming it with your helmet, I assume.
translation.es: No puedes resolverlo a embestidas con tu casco.

translation.en: Every problem can be solved by ramming it with my helmet.
translation.es: Cualquier problema se puede resolver así.

translation.en: We may have a different problem for you to ram.
So the voice in my head led me here to deliver a package.
translation.es: La voz en mi cabeza me envió para entregar un paquete.

translation.en: To who?
You don't happen to have any champions out here, do you?
Being a champion
is about defending those who can't defend themselves.
translation.es: es defender a los que no pueden defenderse.

translation.en: That was weird. Where did that come from?
Are those poacher bots?
Give us the Witch.
Halt. Do not move.
Tiger Tribe answers to no one!
Technology!
I need to protect the village.
We'll find the girl and the sword once everyone's dead.
Duncan, have the robots burn the village.
translation.es: Que los robots quemen la aldea.

translation.en: No, no, no, I--
I can't do that.
Coward.
I'll run out first.
Then you get this as far from here as quickly as you can. Hide it.
translation.es: Luego, llévate esto lejos y rápido. Ocúltalo.

translation.en: If I survive, my voice and I will come back for it.
We need water! Please--
Fire! We need to save the village!
Capture.
Ah, thank you, kind stranger.
Talking tiger!
Whoa! Flying child!
Krass, stand down. He saved me.
Hey, Evelyn.
There she is.
They don't get to attack us and run without a fight.
translation.es: No nos atacan y huyen sin resistencia.

translation.en: Come on, Cringer.
Intercept. Capture.
Contain.
Do not run.
Stop.
Error.
Hang on. I've got you.
Don't worry. This is my favorite cliff.
I almost die here all the time.
I told you to get away from here.
Get the real sword out of here.
I had a sword this whole time?
Hand it over, thief.
You want this? Come and get it.
By the Power of Grayskull, I have the Power?
translation.es: ¿Por el poder de Grayskull, ya tengo el poder?

translation.en: I have the Power!
- What? - No!
What? He's... a man.
The Power of Grayskull.
Will never be yours!
The Power of Grayskull...
...belongs to me!
